am\": \"a sun-drenched home crowd\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given her extensive 32-year Paralympic experience, mother-of-two Storey will be undaunted bywhatever the French capital throws at her.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1128, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9595878279613235, \"rank\": 0.03439069524586045, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her extensive 32-year Paralympic experience\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"mother-of-two Storey\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have competed internationally every year, even in the years when I had children,\\\" she told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am prepared for all eventualities and that's the thing that Tokyo taught everybody.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9697974951784533, \"rank\": 0.027427520235690526, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all eventualities\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In London, when everybody said, 'how are you going to be preparing to compete in front of so many people?\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1468, \"entitie